OL,3,C'Serious concerns' for safety of
OL,4,Cchildren at young offender institution
OL,6,FSerious concerns have been raised for
OL,7,Fthe safety of children - at a young
OL,8,Foffenders institute in Rochester.
OL,10,FAn HM prisons inspector found a "near
OL,11,Ftotal breakdown in behaviour
OL,12,Fmanagement" at Cookham Wood - and
OL,13,Fcalled for a "concerted and urgent
OL,14,Fresponse".
OL,16,FThe Ministry of Justice says it has
OL,17,Fput in place robust plans to improve
OL,18,Fsafety and support for those with
OL,19,Fcomplex needs.
